name: New normal, New style
description:
11 march 2020 W.H.O declared we have pandemic global situation, It’s been 2 Years of global pandemic, and covid already has many of variants, alpha, beta, delta, gamma, omicron, etc. Many things has changed, we changed our life style, everytime we go out we should wear mask. New normal(?) New rules, New style, wear mask save ourself and save the other life’s
Stay safe, stay healthy.
